      "labels": [],
      "body": "## Summary\n\n- Replace \"apples-to-apples\" colloquialism with \"direct, equivalent\" per NIST IR 8366 inclusive language guidance\n- Rewrite companion documents sentence (Section 1.4) to be factual, removing awkward double-SHOULD construction\n- Fix \"terminologies\" \u2192 \"terms\" (Section 2)\n- Fix \"transfering\" typo \u2192 \"transferring\"\n- Fix missing spaces and inconsistent capitalization in e.g. list (Section 3.2)\n- Consolidate duplicate NOTE blocks in KPI framework section (Section 4) into one\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] Verify rendered HTML output looks correct\n- [ ] Confirm no unintended content changes (review diff)",
